502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c9d695956ffd88a0340a86623516ef533d9cd1","tid":183302,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c1d10a26169adc10579d632965ab9ec169e5c9","tid":183302,"uid":14452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:12:55.000Z","msg":"幫下你啦！tg我：TravP"},{"pid":"98699505af25257dd580860bf0fed5787bd6636f","tid":183302,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫下你啦！tg我：TravP</blockquote><br />\n冇TG 係度大概講講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e77f7307d252552b97204fcfd02a3036d682240","tid":183302,"uid":14452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幫下你啦！tg我：TravP</blockquote><br />\n冇TG 係度大概講講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁byebye 等人救你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d671dc98e4f0cb0a4c25245ccc8b67a61837502","tid":183302,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b72cddfe554802225b351ffbb3a677be87885c2","tid":183302,"uid":89477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我用PS拉完線 係PS度睇好多粒星同好光拉到<br />\n<br />\n但一SAVE完後D星就暗返哂同小左好多 <br />\n<br />\n試過save jpg(最大品質) 同png都係咁 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪直接將張相放落PS執?<br />\n如果係既話，我諗應該係AdobeRGB同sRGB既色域問題<br />\n你試下用LR setting揀save/export時用sRGB格式，再export去PS到執應該就會解決到<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"ffac6d071f288778efb3007e1af81f5a4a6aca40","tid":183302,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我用PS拉完線 係PS度睇好多粒星同好光拉到<br />\n<br />\n但一SAVE完後D星就暗返哂同小左好多 <br />\n<br />\n試過save jpg(最大品質) 同png都係咁 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪直接將張相放落PS執?<br />\n如果係既話，我諗應該係AdobeRGB同sRGB既色域問題<br />\n你試下用LR setting揀save/export時用sRGB格式，再export去PS到執應該就會解決到<br />\nsorry for 1999</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打 一陣試<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b3763217772c79ed924895030718c1d2923e0b","tid":183302,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:44:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我用PS拉完線 係PS度睇好多粒星同好光拉到<br />\n<br />\n但一SAVE完後D星就暗返哂同小左好多 <br />\n<br />\n試過save jpg(最大品質) 同png都係咁 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪直接將張相放落PS執?<br />\n如果係既話，我諗應該係AdobeRGB同sRGB既色域問題<br />\n你試下用LR setting揀save/export時用sRGB格式，再export去PS到執應該就會解決到<br />\nsorry for 1999</blockquote><br />\n我搵到原因喇<br />\n因為用PS save時佢會將拉光個圖層 同張相個圖層combine左先save<br />\n但一combine後就變暗左<br />\n有冇巴打識解決  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ac0574c830eb2a8d8164442ac131a7f1b980c1","tid":183302,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T12:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88c2cfec4da0c9d3c32d3ed9e9cede9c7b77ae7","tid":183302,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb5927eba825776f385a3b317a56c7460bdc060","tid":183302,"uid":89477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我用PS拉完線 係PS度睇好多粒星同好光拉到<br />\n<br />\n但一SAVE完後D星就暗返哂同小左好多 <br />\n<br />\n試過save jpg(最大品質) 同png都係咁 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪直接將張相放落PS執?<br />\n如果係既話，我諗應該係AdobeRGB同sRGB既色域問題<br />\n你試下用LR setting揀save/export時用sRGB格式，再export去PS到執應該就會解決到<br />\nsorry for 1999</blockquote><br />\n我搵到原因喇<br />\n因為用PS save時佢會將拉光個圖層 同張相個圖層combine左先save<br />\n但一combine後就變暗左<br />\n有冇巴打識解決  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解要combine先save<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8b07929a434fd196cf278b7fc996f1cc0f37df","tid":183302,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:52:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我用PS拉完線 係PS度睇好多粒星同好光拉到<br />\n<br />\n但一SAVE完後D星就暗返哂同小左好多 <br />\n<br />\n試過save jpg(最大品質) 同png都係咁 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪直接將張相放落PS執?<br />\n如果係既話，我諗應該係AdobeRGB同sRGB既色域問題<br />\n你試下用LR setting揀save/export時用sRGB格式，再export去PS到執應該就會解決到<br />\nsorry for 1999</blockquote><br />\n我搵到原因喇<br />\n因為用PS save時佢會將拉光個圖層 同張相個圖層combine左先save<br />\n但一combine後就變暗左<br />\n有冇巴打識解決  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解要combine先save<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n次次一禁save 佢都自動combine (merge layer)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> save 後又分返開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559b382a621a8076db2afe8949cb9614808a203b","tid":183302,"uid":77663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e317d78c57109614e67152fad92a20a045dd0f","tid":183302,"uid":89477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我用PS拉完線 係PS度睇好多粒星同好光拉到<br />\n<br />\n但一SAVE完後D星就暗返哂同小左好多 <br />\n<br />\n試過save jpg(最大品質) 同png都係咁 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪直接將張相放落PS執?<br />\n如果係既話，我諗應該係AdobeRGB同sRGB既色域問題<br />\n你試下用LR setting揀save/export時用sRGB格式，再export去PS到執應該就會解決到<br />\nsorry for 1999</blockquote><br />\n我搵到原因喇<br />\n因為用PS save時佢會將拉光個圖層 同張相個圖層combine左先save<br />\n但一combine後就變暗左<br />\n有冇巴打識解決  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解要combine先save<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n次次一禁save 佢都自動combine (merge layer)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> save 後又分返開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係好想像到你既情況<br />\n但有個另類D既方法, 你試下save psd檔再你LR export jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}